' Class definitions at top
class ":DetectCommunitiesUI" {
}

class ":ProjectsController" {
}

' Actor and sequence flow
actor "Business User" as User
participant ":DetectCommunitiesUI" as DetectCommunitiesUI
participant ":ProjectsController" as ProjectsController

User -> DetectCommunitiesUI: Request community detection
DetectCommunitiesUI -> ProjectsController: detect_communities()
ProjectsController -> ProjectsController: Run detection algorithm
ProjectsController --> DetectCommunitiesUI: community results
DetectCommunitiesUI --> User: Display detected communities

